author: obiwanfan
title: MY FIRST LEGO SET!
review: This was my first Lego set so unfortunately I don't remember that much about it. It came with a lot of good peices and minifigs and was good for starting a lego collection. It also came with a one of a kind baseplate you could only get with that set that I still use a lot. I would recomend this set for anyone (if you can find it).
